xil_kernel_get_height, xil_kernel_get_width, xil_kernel_get_key_x,  xil_kernel_get_key_y \- read attributes of kernels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.ft B
.nf
#include <xil/xil.h>
.fi
.sp .5v
